pageContext.claim: “If somebody else, let’s say the opponent [Hillary Clinton], who shouldn't even be allowed to run, you know she happens to be a crooked person, so her name is very appropriate but if she ever won our, I would say China right now would be far ahead of the United States, just think of it. China would have been -- we are now so far ahead of China, it’s not even a contest.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump claims implausibly that China would be outperforming the United States economically had Hillary Clinton won the 2016 election.
